Creating Images 13

Select the  to download all the images to use in this dashboard. We will not use the homework or video, we will wait until the end of this dashboard before inserting these.


Step 1: Insert all images into dashboard. Make sure that the 5 items in the second picture are all loaded into the Dashboard from your local computer.





Step 2: Select Colaberry Logo

- Under the visualizations pane choose the drop down on General

- X position = 185, Y position = 0, Width = 159, Height = 79

Step 3: Select Paper with Apple

- Under the visualizations pane choose the drop down on General

- X position = 1121, Y position = 0, Width = 159, Height = 79




Utilize the GIF above if you need help with formatting the next 3 steps. 


Step 4: Select Got Homework Image

- Under the visualizations pane choose the drop down on General

- X position = 231, Y position = 80, Width = 66, Height = 62

Step 5: Select Book with Pencil

- Under the visualizations pane choose the drop down on General

- X position = 591, Y position = 80, Width = 78, Height = 63

Step 6: Select Graded Paper

- Under the visualizations pane choose the drop down on General

- X position = 953, Y position = 80, Width = 78, Height = 62
